<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="World confuse child"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="世惑い子"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="kaf"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かふ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花谱"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Crazy for you"/><amll:meta key="album" value="狂想"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPY392100027"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1674704370"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2026790782"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="3gKbfrRbrCYBpg7YEA6PeK"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="004TZYiU36BfTc"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="399013970"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:48.510"><div begin="6.150" end="3:48.510"><p begin="6.150" end="8.280" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="6.150" end="6.340">一</span><span begin="6.660" end="7.160">体</span><span begin="7.160" end="7.420">どう</span><span begin="7.420" end="7.660">し</span><span begin="7.660" end="7.820">た</span><span begin="7.820" end="8.000">ん</span><span begin="8.000" end="8.150">だ</span><span begin="8.150" end="8.250">い</span><span begin="8.250" end="8.280">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">究竟是怎么了呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">究竟是怎麼了呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What in the world is wrong?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도대체 무슨 일이야？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qu&apos;est-ce qui t&apos;arrive au juste ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Qué es lo que pasa exactamente?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was ist denn eigentlich los?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что же случилось?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che ti prende?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ittai doushitan dai?</span></p><p begin="9.600" end="12.570" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="9.600" end="9.810">そ</span><span begin="9.810" end="9.990">ん</span><span begin="9.990" end="10.170">な</span><span begin="10.170" end="10.320">と</span><span begin="10.320" end="10.490">こ</span><span begin="10.490" end="10.650">ろ</span><span begin="10.650" end="10.990">で</span><span begin="10.990" end="11.640">悩</span><span begin="11.640" end="11.950">ん</span><span begin="11.950" end="12.120">で</span><span begin="12.120" end="12.570">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">独自在那边烦恼着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">獨自在那邊煩惱著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Worrying in a place like that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 곳에서 고민하고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À te tracasser dans un endroit pareil</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Preocupándote en un lugar como ese</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass du dich da so quälst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему ты терзаешься в таком месте</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Preoccuparti in un posto del genere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna tokoro de nayande sa</span></p><p begin="14.180" end="16.310" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.180" end="14.680">何</span><span begin="14.680" end="14.870">が</span><span begin="14.990" end="15.470">辛</span><span begin="15.470" end="15.640">い</span><span begin="15.640" end="15.980">ん</span><span begin="15.980" end="16.150">だ</span><span begin="16.150" end="16.280">い</span><span begin="16.280" end="16.310">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有什么痛苦的呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有什麼痛苦的呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What is so painful?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무엇이 힘든 거야？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qu&apos;est-ce qui est si dur ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Qué es lo que te duele?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was ist so schmerzhaft?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что тебя так мучает?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cosa c&apos;è di doloroso?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nani ga tsurain dai?</span></p><p begin="17.660" end="20.300" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.660" end="17.960">何</span><span begin="17.960" end="18.100">で</span><span begin="18.100" end="18.280">そ</span><span begin="18.280" end="18.470">ん</span><span begin="18.470" end="18.680">な</span><span begin="18.680" end="18.930">に</span><span begin="18.930" end="19.460">震</span><span begin="19.460" end="19.670">え</span><span begin="19.670" end="19.820">て</span><span begin="19.820" end="20.020">ん</span><span begin="20.020" end="20.180">だ</span><span begin="20.180" end="20.270">い</span><span begin="20.270" end="20.300">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么颤抖成那样呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為什麼顫抖成那樣呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why are you trembling so much?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">왜 그렇게 떨고 있는 거야？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi trembles-tu autant ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Por qué estás temblando tanto?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum zitterst du so sehr?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему ты так дрожишь?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché tremi così tanto?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nande sonna ni furueten dai?</span></p><p begin="21.630" end="24.570" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.630" end="21.680">っ</span><span begin="21.680" end="21.970">て</span><span begin="22.160" end="22.290">こ</span><span begin="22.290" end="22.480">ん</span><span begin="22.480" end="22.660">な</span><span begin="22.660" end="23.000">こ</span><span begin="23.000" end="23.190">と</span><span begin="23.190" end="23.340">聞</span><span begin="23.340" end="23.490">く</span><span begin="23.490" end="23.600">こ</span><span begin="23.700" end="23.990">と</span><span begin="23.990" end="24.230">自</span><span begin="24.230" end="24.570">体</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">问出这种话本身</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">問出這種話本身</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">But just asking something like this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">라고 이런 걸 묻는 것 자체가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le simple fait de te demander ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que yo te pregunte este tipo de cosas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass ich solche Dinge überhaupt frage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наверное сами эти расспросы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma il solo fatto di chiederti questo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tte konna koto kiku koto jitai</span></p><p begin="25.640" end="28.400" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.640" end="25.980">君</span><span begin="25.980" end="26.170">に</span><span begin="26.170" end="26.370">と</span><span begin="26.370" end="26.610">っ</span><span begin="26.610" end="26.860">ちゃ</span><span begin="27.020" end="27.430">迷</span><span begin="27.430" end="27.940">惑</span><span begin="27.940" end="28.080">か</span><span begin="28.180" end="28.400">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">对你来说会是种困扰吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對你來說會是種困擾吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Might be annoying to you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너에게는 민폐일까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Te dérange peut-être</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tal vez sea una molestia para ti</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist für dich vielleicht lästig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тебе только в тягость</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Forse ti dà fastidio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ni totcha meiwaku kana</span></p><p begin="29.640" end="33.620" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.640" end="29.820">で</span><span begin="29.820" end="29.960">も</span><span begin="29.960" end="30.480">心</span><span begin="30.480" end="30.630">の</span><span begin="30.630" end="31.160">底</span><span begin="31.160" end="31.490">か</span><span begin="31.490" end="31.590">ら</span><span begin="31.690" end="32.260">迷</span><span begin="32.260" end="32.480">っ</span><span begin="32.480" end="32.660">て</span><span begin="32.660" end="32.950">る</span><span begin="32.950" end="33.490">君</span><span begin="33.490" end="33.620">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但是对打心底感到迷茫的你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但是對打心底感到迷茫的你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">But for you who is lost from the bottom of your heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 진심으로 헤매고 있는 너에게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais pour toi qui es perdu du fond du cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero para ti que estás perdido desde el fondo de tu corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber für dich der du aus tiefstem Herzen verwirrt bist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но для тебя заблудившегося в глубине души</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Però a te che sei perso dal profondo del cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Demo kokoro no soko kara mayotteru kimi ni</span></p><p begin="33.950" end="36.390" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.950" end="34.110">で</span><span begin="34.110" end="34.450">き</span><span begin="34.450" end="34.630">る</span><span begin="34.630" end="34.880">こ</span><span begin="34.980" end="35.160">と</span><span begin="35.160" end="35.450">は</span><span begin="35.450" end="35.670">あ</span><span begin="35.670" end="35.940">る</span><span begin="35.940" end="36.150">か</span><span begin="36.150" end="36.390">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我能做些什么呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我能做些什麼呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is there anything I can do</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">할 수 있는 일이 있을까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Y a-t-il quelque chose que je puisse faire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Habrá algo que yo pueda hacer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gibt es da etwas das ich tun kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Могу ли я хоть что-то сделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">C&apos;è qualcosa che posso fare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dekiru koto wa aru kana</span></p><p begin="37.650" end="41.480" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.650" end="37.960">僕</span><span begin="37.960" end="38.150">ら</span><span begin="38.150" end="38.310">こ</span><span begin="38.310" end="38.430">の</span><span begin="38.430" end="38.990">先</span><span begin="38.990" end="39.150">の</span><span begin="39.150" end="39.310">未</span><span begin="39.310" end="39.650">来</span><span begin="39.650" end="39.870">な</span><span begin="39.870" end="39.970">ん</span><span begin="39.970" end="40.130">て</span><span begin="40.130" end="40.330">わ</span><span begin="40.330" end="40.510">か</span><span begin="40.510" end="40.670">ら</span><span begin="40.670" end="40.840">な</span><span begin="40.840" end="40.990">い</span><span begin="40.990" end="41.200">か</span><span begin="41.200" end="41.480">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们对前方的未来 一无所知啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們對前方的未來 一無所知啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because we don&apos;t know the future ahead</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들 앞으로의 미래 같은 건 모르니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme nous ne connaissons rien de l&apos;avenir qui nous attend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque nosotros no conocemos el futuro que nos espera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil wir die vor uns liegende Zukunft nicht kennen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы не знаем что ждёт нас в будущем поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Poiché non conosciamo il nostro futuro da qui in poi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura kono saki no mirai nante wakaranai kara</span></p><p begin="42.180" end="45.490" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.180" end="42.520">ルー</span><span begin="42.520" end="42.680">ル</span><span begin="42.680" end="42.910">な</span><span begin="42.910" end="43.000">ん</span><span begin="43.000" end="43.160">て</span><span begin="43.160" end="43.320">ど</span><span begin="43.320" end="43.490">こ</span><span begin="43.490" end="43.670">に</span><span begin="43.670" end="43.990">も</span><span begin="43.990" end="44.180">な</span><span begin="44.180" end="44.480">い</span><span begin="44.480" end="44.660">ん</span><span begin="44.660" end="44.970">だ</span><span begin="44.970" end="45.180">か</span><span begin="45.180" end="45.490">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">规则这种东西 哪里都不存在啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">規則這種東西 哪裡都不存在啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because there are no rules anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">룰 같은 건 어디에도 없으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et qu&apos;il n&apos;y a de règles nulle part</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque no hay reglas en ninguna parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil es nirgendwo Regeln gibt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Никаких правил нигде не существует поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E le regole non esistono da nessuna parte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ruuru nante doko ni mo nain dakara</span></p><p begin="46.070" end="49.430" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.070" end="46.300">好</span><span begin="46.300" end="46.480">き</span><span begin="46.480" end="46.640">な</span><span begin="46.640" end="46.810">こ</span><span begin="46.810" end="46.960">と</span><span begin="46.960" end="47.120">を</span><span begin="47.120" end="47.300">好</span><span begin="47.300" end="47.480">き</span><span begin="47.480" end="47.660">と</span><span begin="47.660" end="47.820">言</span><span begin="47.820" end="47.990">っ</span><span begin="47.990" end="48.210">て</span><span begin="48.210" end="48.350">い</span><span begin="48.350" end="48.680">い</span><span begin="48.680" end="48.980">ん</span><span begin="48.980" end="49.180">だ</span><span begin="49.180" end="49.430">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喜欢的事物 就大声说喜欢吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喜歡的事物 就大聲說喜歡吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to say you like what you like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">좋아하는 걸 좋아한다고 말해도 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as le droit de dire que tu aimes ce que tu aimes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Está bien decir que te gusta lo que te gusta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Darfst du sagen dass du magst was du magst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты можешь смело говорить что любишь то что любишь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Puoi dire che ti piace ciò che ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukina koto o suki to itte iin da yo</span></p><p begin="50.100" end="53.410" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.100" end="50.320">好</span><span begin="50.320" end="50.480">き</span><span begin="50.480" end="50.650">な</span><span begin="50.650" end="50.840">こ</span><span begin="50.840" end="50.940">と</span><span begin="50.940" end="51.120">を</span><span begin="51.120" end="51.310">好</span><span begin="51.310" end="51.500">き</span><span begin="51.500" end="51.660">に</span><span begin="51.660" end="51.870">や</span><span begin="51.870" end="51.990">っ</span><span begin="51.990" end="52.150">て</span><span begin="52.150" end="52.330">い</span><span begin="52.330" end="52.700">い</span><span begin="52.700" end="53.000">ん</span><span begin="53.000" end="53.180">だ</span><span begin="53.180" end="53.410">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喜欢的事物 就尽情去做吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喜歡的事物 就盡情去做吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to do what you like however you like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">좋아하는 걸 마음대로 해도 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as le droit de faire ce qu&apos;il te plaît comme il te plaît</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Está bien hacer lo que te gusta como te gusta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Darfst du tun und lassen was du magst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты можешь смело делать то что любишь так как хочешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Puoi fare ciò che ti piace come ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukina koto o suki ni yatte iin da yo</span></p><p begin="53.960" end="56.300" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.960" end="54.350">一</span><span begin="54.460" end="54.660">つ</span><span begin="54.660" end="54.980">だ</span><span begin="54.980" end="55.230">け</span><span begin="55.230" end="55.500">あ</span><span begin="55.500" end="55.670">る</span><span begin="55.670" end="56.010">だ</span><span begin="56.010" end="56.300">ろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只有一样东西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只有一樣東西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There must be just one thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">딱 하나 있잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il y a bien une seule chose n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debe haber solo una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es gibt doch sicher diese eine Sache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но есть ведь что-то одно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ci sarà almeno una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hitotsu dake aru darou</span></p><p begin="57.660" end="1:01.050" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.660" end="58.170">心</span><span begin="58.170" end="58.460">の</span><span begin="58.460" end="59.000">奥</span><span begin="59.000" end="59.170">に</span><span begin="59.170" end="59.690">眠</span><span begin="59.690" end="59.990">る</span><span begin="59.990" end="1:00.460">何</span><span begin="1:00.460" end="1:00.690">か</span><span begin="1:00.690" end="1:01.050">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">沉睡在内心深处的 某种事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">沉睡在內心深處的 某種事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Something sleeping deep in your heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음속 깊은 곳에 잠든 무언가가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelque chose qui sommeille au fond de ton cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Algo que duerme en el fondo de tu corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendetwas das tief in deinem Herzen schlummert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что-то дремлющее в глубине твоего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualcosa che dorme nel profondo del cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no oku ni nemuru nanika ga</span></p><p begin="1:01.590" end="1:05.740" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.590" end="1:01.820">そ</span><span begin="1:01.820" end="1:01.970">れ</span><span begin="1:01.970" end="1:02.130">は</span><span begin="1:02.130" end="1:02.460">愛</span><span begin="1:02.460" end="1:02.660">か</span><span begin="1:02.660" end="1:02.910">も</span><span begin="1:02.910" end="1:03.150">し</span><span begin="1:03.150" end="1:03.490">れ</span><span begin="1:03.490" end="1:03.590">な</span><span begin="1:03.590" end="1:03.680">い</span> <span begin="1:04.000" end="1:04.300">憎</span><span begin="1:04.300" end="1:04.510">し</span><span begin="1:04.510" end="1:04.660">み</span><span begin="1:04.660" end="1:04.830">か</span><span begin="1:04.830" end="1:04.950">も</span><span begin="1:04.950" end="1:05.150">し</span><span begin="1:05.150" end="1:05.490">れ</span><span begin="1:05.490" end="1:05.670">な</span><span begin="1:05.670" end="1:05.740">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那或许是爱 或许是憎恨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那或許是愛 或許是憎恨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That might be love or it might be hatred</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그건 사랑일지도 몰라 증오일지도 몰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est peut-être de l&apos;amour ou peut-être de la haine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eso podría ser amor o podría ser odio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es mag Liebe sein es mag Hass sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Может быть это любовь а может быть ненависть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Potrebbe essere amore o forse odio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore wa ai kamo shirenai nikushimi kamo shirenai</span></p><p begin="1:06.150" end="1:08.420" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.150" end="1:06.470">君</span><span begin="1:06.470" end="1:06.650">が</span><span begin="1:06.650" end="1:06.830">決</span><span begin="1:06.830" end="1:06.990">め</span><span begin="1:06.990" end="1:07.120">て</span><span begin="1:07.120" end="1:07.310">い</span><span begin="1:07.310" end="1:07.640">い</span><span begin="1:07.640" end="1:07.990">ん</span><span begin="1:07.990" end="1:08.180">だ</span><span begin="1:08.180" end="1:08.420">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">由你来决定就好哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">由你來決定就好哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay for you to decide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 정해도 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est à toi de décider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Está bien que tú lo decidas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du darfst das entscheiden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это решать только тебе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Puoi deciderlo tu</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga kimete iin da yo</span></p><p begin="1:26.160" end="1:32.380" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.160" end="1:26.360">舐</span><span begin="1:26.490" end="1:26.670">め</span><span begin="1:26.670" end="1:26.970">ら</span><span begin="1:26.970" end="1:27.160">れ</span><span begin="1:27.160" end="1:27.440">る</span><span begin="1:27.440" end="1:27.660">こ</span><span begin="1:27.660" end="1:27.970">と</span><span begin="1:27.970" end="1:28.280">や</span><span begin="1:30.160" end="1:30.350">見</span><span begin="1:30.470" end="1:30.920">下</span><span begin="1:30.920" end="1:31.150">さ</span><span begin="1:31.150" end="1:31.450">れ</span><span begin="1:31.450" end="1:31.650">る</span><span begin="1:31.650" end="1:32.010">こ</span><span begin="1:32.010" end="1:32.380">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被人轻视 被人看不起</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被人輕視 被人看不起</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Being underestimated or being looked down upon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무시당하는 것이나 얕보이는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se faire rabaisser ou se faire mépriser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ser subestimado o ser menospreciado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unterschätzt zu werden oder herabgesehen zu werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда тебя ни во что не ставят или смотрят свысока</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Essere sottovalutati o guardati dall&apos;alto in basso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namerareru koto ya mikudasareru koto</span></p><p begin="1:34.100" end="1:40.230" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.100" end="1:34.380">そ</span><span begin="1:34.380" end="1:34.690">ん</span><span begin="1:34.690" end="1:34.970">な</span><span begin="1:34.970" end="1:35.190">こ</span><span begin="1:35.190" end="1:35.450">と</span><span begin="1:35.450" end="1:35.680">ば</span><span begin="1:35.680" end="1:36.020">か</span><span begin="1:36.020" end="1:36.280">り</span><span begin="1:37.920" end="1:38.170">気</span><span begin="1:38.170" end="1:38.390">に</span><span begin="1:38.390" end="1:38.540">し</span><span begin="1:38.640" end="1:38.930">て</span><span begin="1:38.930" end="1:39.070">し</span><span begin="1:39.180" end="1:39.500">ま</span><span begin="1:39.500" end="1:39.660">う</span><span begin="1:39.660" end="1:40.000">よ</span><span begin="1:40.000" end="1:40.230">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总是会去在意这些事情呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總是會去在意這些事情呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You end up caring only about things like that right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 것만 신경 쓰게 되지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu finis par ne te soucier que de ça n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Terminas preocupándote solo por ese tipo de cosas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Um solche Dinge machst du dir immerzu Sorgen nicht wahr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты ведь только об этом и переживаешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Finisci per preoccuparti solo di queste cose vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna koto bakari ki ni shite shimau yo na</span></p><p begin="1:42.190" end="1:48.320" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.190" end="1:42.680">周</span><span begin="1:42.680" end="1:42.890">り</span><span begin="1:42.990" end="1:43.180">の</span><span begin="1:43.180" end="1:43.470">目</span><span begin="1:43.470" end="1:43.680">ば</span><span begin="1:43.680" end="1:44.020">か</span><span begin="1:44.020" end="1:44.280">り</span><span begin="1:45.950" end="1:46.440">感</span><span begin="1:46.440" end="1:46.650">じ</span><span begin="1:46.650" end="1:46.930">て</span><span begin="1:46.930" end="1:47.150">し</span><span begin="1:47.150" end="1:47.420">ま</span><span begin="1:47.420" end="1:47.690">う</span><span begin="1:47.690" end="1:48.000">の</span><span begin="1:48.000" end="1:48.320">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总是去在意周围的目光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總是去在意周圍的目光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Feeling nothing but the eyes of those around you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">주위의 시선만 의식하게 되는 건</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne ressentir que le regard des autres</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sentir siempre las miradas de los demás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass du immer nur die Blicke der anderen spürst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что ты постоянно чувствуешь на себе взгляды окружающих</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sentire sempre gli occhi degli altri addosso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mawari no me bakari kanjite shimau no wa</span></p><p begin="1:50.060" end="1:56.270" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.060" end="1:50.440">そ</span><span begin="1:50.440" end="1:50.650">ん</span><span begin="1:50.650" end="1:51.010">な</span><span begin="1:51.010" end="1:51.200">に</span><span begin="1:51.200" end="1:51.440">い</span><span begin="1:51.440" end="1:51.690">け</span><span begin="1:51.690" end="1:52.010">な</span><span begin="1:52.010" end="1:52.280">い</span><span begin="1:54.120" end="1:54.380">こ</span><span begin="1:54.480" end="1:54.660">と</span><span begin="1:54.660" end="1:54.910">で</span><span begin="1:54.910" end="1:55.190">は</span><span begin="1:55.190" end="1:55.430">な</span><span begin="1:55.430" end="1:55.570">い</span><span begin="1:55.680" end="1:56.030">か</span><span begin="1:56.030" end="1:56.270">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这并不是什么大不了的坏事啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這並不是什麼大不了的壞事啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is not such a bad thing so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그렇게 나쁜 일은 아니니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n&apos;est pas une si mauvaise chose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No es algo tan malo después de todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist gar nicht so etwas Schlimmes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это не так уж и плохо поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non è poi una cosa così sbagliata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sonna ni ikenai koto de wa nai kara</span></p><p begin="1:57.640" end="2:01.520" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.640" end="1:58.160">心</span><span begin="1:58.160" end="1:58.460">の</span><span begin="1:58.460" end="1:59.010">奥</span><span begin="1:59.010" end="1:59.160">に</span><span begin="1:59.160" end="1:59.480">眠</span><span begin="1:59.480" end="1:59.650">る</span><span begin="1:59.650" end="1:59.950">大</span><span begin="1:59.950" end="2:00.490">切</span><span begin="2:00.490" end="2:00.670">な</span><span begin="2:00.670" end="2:01.000">も</span><span begin="2:01.000" end="2:01.200">の</span><span begin="2:01.200" end="2:01.520">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">沉睡在内心深处的 珍贵事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">沉睡在內心深處的 珍貴事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The precious thing sleeping deep in your heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음속 깊은 곳에 잠든 소중한 것은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les choses précieuses qui sommeillent au fond de ton cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa cosa importante que duerme en el fondo de tu corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Wichtige das tief in deinem Herzen schlummert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То важное что дремлет в глубине твоего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le cose importanti che dormono nel profondo del cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no oku ni nemuru taisetsu na mono wa</span></p><p begin="2:02.120" end="2:05.500" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.120" end="2:02.320">し</span><span begin="2:02.320" end="2:02.490">っ</span><span begin="2:02.490" end="2:02.680">か</span><span begin="2:02.680" end="2:02.980">り</span><span begin="2:02.980" end="2:03.470">両</span><span begin="2:03.470" end="2:03.690">手</span><span begin="2:03.690" end="2:03.970">に</span><span begin="2:03.970" end="2:04.390">抱</span><span begin="2:04.390" end="2:04.650">え</span><span begin="2:04.650" end="2:04.940">て</span><span begin="2:04.940" end="2:05.160">ほ</span><span begin="2:05.160" end="2:05.500">しい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">希望你能用双手紧紧抱住</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">希望你能用雙手緊緊抱住</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want you to hold it firmly in both hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꽉 양손에 안아주었으면 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux que tu les tiennes fermement dans tes deux mains</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero que la sostengas firmemente con ambas manos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sollst du fest in beiden Händen halten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу чтобы ты крепко держал обеими руками</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio che le stringi forte con entrambe le mani</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shikkari ryoute ni kakaete hoshii</span></p><p begin="2:06.110" end="2:09.500" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:06.110" end="2:06.300">そ</span><span begin="2:06.300" end="2:06.480">れ</span><span begin="2:06.480" end="2:06.660">だ</span><span begin="2:06.660" end="2:06.940">け</span><span begin="2:06.940" end="2:07.160">は</span><span begin="2:07.160" end="2:07.450">大</span><span begin="2:07.450" end="2:07.680">事</span><span begin="2:07.680" end="2:07.950">に</span><span begin="2:07.950" end="2:08.450">愛</span><span begin="2:08.450" end="2:08.680">し</span><span begin="2:08.680" end="2:08.900">て</span><span begin="2:08.900" end="2:09.150">ほ</span><span begin="2:09.150" end="2:09.500">しい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯独那个希望你能好好去爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯獨那個希望你能好好去愛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want you to cherish and love only that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것만큼은 소중히 사랑해 주었으면 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux que tu aimes précieusement au moins cela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero que atesores y ames solo eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur das sollst du wertschätzen und lieben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу чтобы ты бережно любил только это</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio che ami con cura almeno quelle</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore dake wa daiji ni aishite hoshii</span></p><p begin="2:10.090" end="2:13.470" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.090" end="2:10.340">世</span><span begin="2:10.340" end="2:10.700">界</span><span begin="2:10.700" end="2:10.830">を</span><span begin="2:10.830" end="2:11.140">滅</span><span begin="2:11.140" end="2:11.350">ぼ</span><span begin="2:11.350" end="2:11.480">し</span><span begin="2:11.480" end="2:11.650">て</span><span begin="2:11.650" end="2:11.830">も</span><span begin="2:12.100" end="2:12.630">しょう</span><span begin="2:12.630" end="2:12.970">が</span><span begin="2:12.970" end="2:13.180">な</span><span begin="2:13.180" end="2:13.470">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就算毁灭世界也无可奈何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就算毀滅世界也無可奈何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It can&apos;t be helped even if it destroys the world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">세계를 멸망시켜도 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si cela doit détruire le monde on n&apos;y peut rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si destruye el mundo no se puede evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn es die Welt zerstört lässt es sich nicht ändern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если это погубит мир ничего не поделаешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non c&apos;è niente da fare anche se distruggi il mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sekai o horoboshite mo shou ga nai</span></p><p begin="2:13.930" end="2:16.350" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:13.930" end="2:14.450">一</span><span begin="2:14.450" end="2:14.640">つ</span><span begin="2:14.640" end="2:14.990">だ</span><span begin="2:14.990" end="2:15.190">け</span><span begin="2:15.190" end="2:15.500">あ</span><span begin="2:15.500" end="2:15.670">る</span><span begin="2:15.670" end="2:16.030">だ</span><span begin="2:16.030" end="2:16.350">ろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只有一样东西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只有一樣東西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There must be just one thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">딱 하나 있잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il y a bien une seule chose n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debe haber solo una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es gibt doch sicher diese eine Sache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но есть ведь что-то одно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ci sarà almeno una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hitotsu dake aru darou</span></p><p begin="2:17.630" end="2:21.030" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.630" end="2:17.990">息</span><span begin="2:17.990" end="2:18.150">を</span><span begin="2:18.150" end="2:18.650">潜</span><span begin="2:18.650" end="2:18.930">め</span><span begin="2:18.930" end="2:19.650">蠢</span><span begin="2:19.650" end="2:19.980">く</span><span begin="2:19.980" end="2:20.480">何</span><span begin="2:20.480" end="2:20.690">か</span><span begin="2:20.690" end="2:21.030">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">屏住呼吸蠢蠢欲动的 某种事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">屏住呼吸蠢蠢欲動的 某種事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Something writhing with bated breath</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">숨을 죽이고 꿈틀대는 무언가가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelque chose qui s&apos;agite en retenant son souffle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Algo que se agita conteniendo la respiración</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendetwas das mit angehaltenem Atem wimmelt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что-то копошащееся и затаившее дыхание</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualcosa che si agita trattenendo il respiro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Iki o hisome ugomeku nanika ga</span></p><p begin="2:21.580" end="2:25.730" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.580" end="2:21.820">そ</span><span begin="2:21.820" end="2:21.960">れ</span><span begin="2:21.960" end="2:22.170">は</span><span begin="2:22.170" end="2:22.470">未</span><span begin="2:22.470" end="2:22.990">来</span><span begin="2:22.990" end="2:23.180">な</span><span begin="2:23.180" end="2:23.470">の</span><span begin="2:23.470" end="2:23.670">か</span> <span begin="2:23.990" end="2:24.160">過</span><span begin="2:24.160" end="2:24.650">去</span><span begin="2:24.650" end="2:24.980">な</span><span begin="2:24.980" end="2:25.190">の</span><span begin="2:25.190" end="2:25.500">か</span><span begin="2:25.500" end="2:25.730">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那究竟是未来 还是过去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那究竟是未來 還是過去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Whether that is the future or the past</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것이 미래인지 과거인지는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Est-ce l&apos;avenir ou bien le passé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si eso es el futuro o es el pasado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ob das die Zukunft ist oder die Vergangenheit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Будущее ли это или прошлое</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se sia il futuro o il passato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore wa mirai na no ka kako na no ka wa</span></p><p begin="2:26.150" end="2:28.430" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.150" end="2:26.470">君</span><span begin="2:26.470" end="2:26.670">だ</span><span begin="2:26.670" end="2:26.980">け</span><span begin="2:26.980" end="2:27.140">が</span><span begin="2:27.140" end="2:27.440">知</span><span begin="2:27.440" end="2:27.680">っ</span><span begin="2:27.680" end="2:27.970">て</span><span begin="2:27.970" end="2:28.160">い</span><span begin="2:28.160" end="2:28.430">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只有你知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只有你知曉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Only you know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너만이 알고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toi seul le sais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo tú lo sabes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weißt nur du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Знаешь только ты</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lo sai solo tu</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi dake ga shitte iru</span></p><p begin="2:45.660" end="2:49.300" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.660" end="2:45.980">逃</span><span begin="2:45.980" end="2:46.190">げ</span><span begin="2:46.190" end="2:46.650">る</span><span begin="2:46.650" end="2:46.890">こ</span><span begin="2:46.990" end="2:47.370">と</span> <span begin="2:47.660" end="2:48.480">戦</span><span begin="2:48.480" end="2:48.650">う</span><span begin="2:48.650" end="2:48.870">こ</span><span begin="2:48.970" end="2:49.300">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">逃避 战斗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">逃避 戰鬥</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Running away fighting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도망치는 것 싸우는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fuir se battre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Huir o luchar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zu fliehen zu kämpfen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сбегать или сражаться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fuggire combattere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nigeru koto tatakau koto</span></p><p begin="2:49.650" end="2:53.210" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:49.650" end="2:50.140">殺</span><span begin="2:50.140" end="2:50.650">す</span><span begin="2:50.650" end="2:50.980">こ</span><span begin="2:50.980" end="2:51.220">と</span> <span begin="2:51.630" end="2:52.120">許</span><span begin="2:52.120" end="2:52.630">す</span><span begin="2:52.630" end="2:52.980">こ</span><span begin="2:52.980" end="2:53.210">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">杀戮 宽恕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">殺戮 寬恕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Killing forgiving</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">죽이는 것 용서하는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tuer pardonner</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Matar o perdonar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zu töten zu vergeben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Убивать или прощать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Uccidere perdonare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Korosu koto yurusu koto</span></p><p begin="2:53.620" end="2:57.490" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.620" end="2:54.160">愛</span><span begin="2:54.160" end="2:54.450">す</span><span begin="2:54.450" end="2:54.650">る</span><span begin="2:54.650" end="2:54.880">こ</span><span begin="2:55.000" end="2:55.260">と</span> <span begin="2:55.660" end="2:56.160">信</span><span begin="2:56.160" end="2:56.520">じ</span><span begin="2:56.520" end="2:56.670">合</span><span begin="2:56.670" end="2:57.000">う</span><span begin="2:57.000" end="2:57.210">こ</span><span begin="2:57.210" end="2:57.490">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">相爱 互信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">相愛 互信</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Loving believing in each other</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑하는 것 서로 믿는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Aimer croire l&apos;un en l&apos;autre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Amar o creer el uno en el otro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zu lieben einander zu vertrauen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Любить или верить друг другу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Amare credere l&apos;uno nell&apos;altro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aisuru koto shinjiau koto</span></p><p begin="2:58.130" end="3:01.420" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.130" end="2:58.700">しょう</span><span begin="2:58.700" end="2:59.000">も</span><span begin="2:59.000" end="2:59.180">な</span><span begin="2:59.180" end="2:59.470">い</span><span begin="2:59.470" end="2:59.670">こ</span><span begin="2:59.670" end="2:59.990">と</span><span begin="2:59.990" end="3:00.140">で</span><span begin="3:00.140" end="3:00.700">笑</span><span begin="3:00.700" end="3:00.860">う</span><span begin="3:00.960" end="3:01.180">こ</span><span begin="3:01.180" end="3:01.420">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为无聊的小事而欢笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為無聊的小事而歡笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Laughing at trivial things</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하잘것없는 일로 웃는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rire pour des choses insignifiantes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Reírse por cosas sin importancia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Über bedeutungslose Dinge zu lachen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смеяться над всякими глупостями</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ridere per cose stupide</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shoumonai koto de warau koto</span></p><p begin="3:01.930" end="3:05.760" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:01.930" end="3:02.190">そ</span><span begin="3:02.190" end="3:02.440">の</span><span begin="3:02.440" end="3:02.980">全</span><span begin="3:02.980" end="3:03.200">て</span><span begin="3:03.200" end="3:03.350">に</span><span begin="3:03.650" end="3:03.890">価</span><span begin="3:04.000" end="3:04.180">値</span><span begin="3:04.180" end="3:04.480">を</span><span begin="3:04.480" end="3:04.710">決</span><span begin="3:04.710" end="3:04.970">め</span><span begin="3:04.970" end="3:05.200">る</span><span begin="3:05.200" end="3:05.520">の</span><span begin="3:05.520" end="3:05.760">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">决定这一切价值的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">決定這一切價值的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The one who decides the value of all of that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 모든 것에 가치를 정하는 건</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celui qui décide de la valeur de tout cela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quien decide el valor de todo eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wer den Wert all dessen bestimmt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ценность всего этого определяешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">A decidere il valore di tutto questo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono subete ni kachi o kimeru no wa</span></p><p begin="3:06.180" end="3:08.920" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:06.180" end="3:06.660">紛</span><span begin="3:06.660" end="3:06.870">れ</span><span begin="3:06.970" end="3:07.110">も</span><span begin="3:07.210" end="3:07.350">な</span><span begin="3:07.350" end="3:07.550">い</span><span begin="3:07.650" end="3:08.160">君</span><span begin="3:08.160" end="3:08.470">だ</span><span begin="3:08.470" end="3:08.700">か</span><span begin="3:08.700" end="3:08.920">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是确凿无疑的你啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是確鑿無疑的你啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is unmistakably you so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">틀림없는 너니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est indéniablement toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eres innegablemente tú</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bist zweifellos du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Несомненно только ты поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sei inequivocabilmente tu</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Magire mo nai kimi dakara</span></p><p begin="3:09.600" end="3:11.100" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:09.600" end="3:10.170">そう</span><span begin="3:10.170" end="3:10.480">だ</span><span begin="3:10.480" end="3:10.710">ろ</span><span begin="3:10.710" end="3:11.100">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是这样吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是這樣吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Isn&apos;t that right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그렇잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">N&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nicht wahr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не так ли?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non è così</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sou darou</span></p><p begin="3:17.650" end="3:21.510" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:17.650" end="3:17.990">僕</span><span begin="3:17.990" end="3:18.160">ら</span><span begin="3:18.160" end="3:18.340">こ</span><span begin="3:18.340" end="3:18.450">の</span><span begin="3:18.450" end="3:19.000">先</span><span begin="3:19.000" end="3:19.180">の</span><span begin="3:19.180" end="3:19.310">未</span><span begin="3:19.310" end="3:19.670">来</span><span begin="3:19.670" end="3:19.830">な</span><span begin="3:19.830" end="3:19.970">ん</span><span begin="3:19.970" end="3:20.120">て</span><span begin="3:20.120" end="3:20.330">わ</span><span begin="3:20.330" end="3:20.510">か</span><span begin="3:20.510" end="3:20.700">ら</span><span begin="3:20.700" end="3:20.810">な</span><span begin="3:20.810" end="3:20.990">い</span><span begin="3:20.990" end="3:21.200">か</span><span begin="3:21.200" end="3:21.510">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们对前方的未来 一无所知啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們對前方的未來 一無所知啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because we don&apos;t know the future ahead</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들 앞으로의 미래 같은 건 모르니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme nous ne connaissons rien de l&apos;avenir qui nous attend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque nosotros no conocemos el futuro que nos espera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil wir die vor uns liegende Zukunft nicht kennen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы не знаем что ждёт нас в будущем поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Poiché non conosciamo il nostro futuro da qui in poi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura kono saki no mirai nante wakaranai kara</span></p><p begin="3:22.170" end="3:25.420" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:22.170" end="3:22.500">ルー</span><span begin="3:22.500" end="3:22.700">ル</span><span begin="3:22.700" end="3:22.870">な</span><span begin="3:22.870" end="3:22.990">ん</span><span begin="3:22.990" end="3:23.160">て</span><span begin="3:23.160" end="3:23.320">ど</span><span begin="3:23.320" end="3:23.500">こ</span><span begin="3:23.500" end="3:23.700">に</span><span begin="3:23.700" end="3:24.000">も</span><span begin="3:24.000" end="3:24.160">な</span><span begin="3:24.160" end="3:24.430">い</span><span begin="3:24.430" end="3:24.630">ん</span><span begin="3:24.630" end="3:24.910">だ</span><span begin="3:24.910" end="3:25.190">か</span><span begin="3:25.190" end="3:25.420">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">规则这种东西 哪里都不存在啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">規則這種東西 哪裡都不存在啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because there are no rules anywhere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">룰 같은 건 어디에도 없으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et qu&apos;il n&apos;y a de règles nulle part</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque no hay reglas en ninguna parte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil es nirgendwo Regeln gibt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Никаких правил нигде не существует поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E le regole non esistono da nessuna parte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ruuru nante doko ni mo nain dakara</span></p><p begin="3:26.080" end="3:29.370" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:26.080" end="3:26.300">好</span><span begin="3:26.300" end="3:26.490">き</span><span begin="3:26.490" end="3:26.650">な</span><span begin="3:26.650" end="3:26.820">こ</span><span begin="3:26.820" end="3:26.940">と</span><span begin="3:26.940" end="3:27.150">を</span><span begin="3:27.150" end="3:27.300">好</span><span begin="3:27.300" end="3:27.500">き</span><span begin="3:27.500" end="3:27.690">と</span><span begin="3:27.690" end="3:27.830">言</span><span begin="3:27.830" end="3:27.980">っ</span><span begin="3:27.980" end="3:28.150">て</span><span begin="3:28.150" end="3:28.280">い</span><span begin="3:28.280" end="3:28.630">い</span><span begin="3:28.730" end="3:28.940">ん</span><span begin="3:28.940" end="3:29.150">だ</span><span begin="3:29.150" end="3:29.370">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喜欢的事物 就大声说喜欢吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喜歡的事物 就大聲說喜歡吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to say you like what you like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">좋아하는 걸 좋아한다고 말해도 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as le droit de dire que tu aimes ce que tu aimes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Está bien decir que te gusta lo que te gusta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Darfst du sagen dass du magst was du magst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты можешь смело говорить что любишь то что любишь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Puoi dire che ti piace ciò che ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukina koto o suki to itte iin da yo</span></p><p begin="3:30.110" end="3:33.410" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.110" end="3:30.310">好</span><span begin="3:30.310" end="3:30.490">き</span><span begin="3:30.490" end="3:30.650">な</span><span begin="3:30.650" end="3:30.840">こ</span><span begin="3:30.840" end="3:30.960">と</span><span begin="3:30.960" end="3:31.140">を</span><span begin="3:31.140" end="3:31.320">好</span><span begin="3:31.320" end="3:31.520">き</span><span begin="3:31.520" end="3:31.660">に</span><span begin="3:31.660" end="3:31.820">や</span><span begin="3:31.820" end="3:31.990">っ</span><span begin="3:31.990" end="3:32.140">て</span><span begin="3:32.140" end="3:32.300">い</span><span begin="3:32.300" end="3:32.670">い</span><span begin="3:32.670" end="3:32.980">ん</span><span begin="3:32.980" end="3:33.160">だ</span><span begin="3:33.160" end="3:33.410">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喜欢的事物 就尽情去做吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喜歡的事物 就盡情去做吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s okay to do what you like however you like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">좋아하는 걸 마음대로 해도 돼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as le droit de faire ce qu&apos;il te plaît comme il te plaît</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Está bien hacer lo que te gusta como te gusta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Darfst du tun und lassen was du magst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты можешь смело делать то что любишь так как хочешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Puoi fare ciò che ti piace come ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukina koto o suki ni yatte iin da yo</span></p><p begin="3:33.950" end="3:36.400" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:33.950" end="3:34.480">一</span><span begin="3:34.480" end="3:34.670">つ</span><span begin="3:34.670" end="3:35.000">だ</span><span begin="3:35.000" end="3:35.200">け</span><span begin="3:35.200" end="3:35.520">あ</span><span begin="3:35.520" end="3:35.680">る</span><span begin="3:35.680" end="3:36.000">だ</span><span begin="3:36.000" end="3:36.400">ろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只有一样东西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只有一樣東西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There must be just one thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">딱 하나 있잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il y a bien une seule chose n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debe haber solo una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es gibt doch sicher diese eine Sache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но есть ведь что-то одно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ci sarà almeno una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hitotsu dake aru darou</span></p><p begin="3:37.660" end="3:41.040" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:37.660" end="3:37.880">焦</span><span begin="3:37.880" end="3:38.050">が</span><span begin="3:38.050" end="3:38.200">れ</span><span begin="3:38.200" end="3:38.460">る</span><span begin="3:38.460" end="3:38.700">ほ</span><span begin="3:38.700" end="3:38.950">ど</span><span begin="3:38.950" end="3:39.470">描</span><span begin="3:39.470" end="3:39.670">い</span><span begin="3:39.670" end="3:40.000">た</span><span begin="3:40.000" end="3:40.490">何</span><span begin="3:40.490" end="3:40.690">か</span><span begin="3:40.690" end="3:41.040">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">渴望到魂牵梦萦的 某种事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">渴望到魂牽夢縈的 某種事物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Something you painted so much you yearned for it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애가 탈 정도로 그렸던 무언가가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelque chose que tu as dessiné avec tant d&apos;ardeur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Algo que dibujaste hasta anhelarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendetwas das du dir so sehnsüchtig ausgemalt hast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что-то что ты рисовал с таким нетерпением</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualcosa che hai disegnato fino a struggerti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kogareru hodo egaita nanika ga</span></p><p begin="3:41.590" end="3:45.670" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:41.590" end="3:41.820">そ</span><span begin="3:41.820" end="3:41.990">れ</span><span begin="3:41.990" end="3:42.170">は</span><span begin="3:42.170" end="3:42.500">い</span><span begin="3:42.500" end="3:42.690">ず</span><span begin="3:42.690" end="3:42.960">れ</span><span begin="3:42.960" end="3:43.170">世</span><span begin="3:43.170" end="3:43.490">界</span><span begin="3:43.490" end="3:43.670">を</span><span begin="3:44.000" end="3:44.950">覆</span><span begin="3:44.950" end="3:45.150">す</span><span begin="3:45.150" end="3:45.340">こ</span><span begin="3:45.340" end="3:45.510">と</span><span begin="3:45.510" end="3:45.670">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那迟早会颠覆世界这件事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那遲早會顛覆世界這件事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That it will eventually overturn the world</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것이 언젠가 세계를 뒤집을 것이란 걸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que cela finira par renverser le monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que eso eventualmente volcará el mundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass es eines Tages die Welt umstürzen wird</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что однажды это перевернёт мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che prima o poi ribalterà il mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore wa izure sekai o kutsugaesu koto o</span></p><p begin="3:46.180" end="3:48.510" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:46.180" end="3:46.510">君</span><span begin="3:46.510" end="3:46.710">だ</span><span begin="3:46.710" end="3:47.010">け</span><span begin="3:47.010" end="3:47.210">が</span><span begin="3:47.210" end="3:47.500">知</span><span begin="3:47.500" end="3:47.710">っ</span><span begin="3:47.710" end="3:47.960">て</span><span begin="3:47.960" end="3:48.200">い</span><span begin="3:48.200" end="3:48.510">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只有你知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只有你知曉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Only you know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너만이 알고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toi seul le sais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo tú lo sabes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weißt nur du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Знаешь только ты</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lo sai solo tu</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi dake ga shitte iru</span></p></div></body></tt>